          "date": "2025-08-04 18:57:54.000000000",
          "tz": 540
        },
        "subject": "LU-19233 build: add system-sb-certs as a buildreq",
        "message": "LU-19233 build: add system-sb-certs as a buildreq\n\nThe Jenkins build has failed with el8.10(inkernel) because the\n\"system-sb-certs\" package dependency specification is missing.\n\nSo this patch adds the \"system-sb-certs\" package to the RPM\nspec file as a BuildRequires dependency.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial fstype=zfs mdtcount=4 mdscount=2 \\\n    clientdistro=el8.10 serverdistro=el8.10 testlist=sanity\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial fstype=zfs mdtcount=4 mdscount=2 \\\n    clientdistro=el9.5 serverdistro=el9.5 testlist=sanity\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial fstype=zfs mdtcount=4 mdscount=2 \\\n    clientdistro=el9.5 serverdistro=el9.5 testgroup=full-dne-zfs-part-1\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial optional fstype=zfs mdtcount=4 mdscount=2 \\\n    clientdistro=el9.5 serverdistro=el9.5 testgroup=full-dne-zfs-part-2\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial fstype=zfs mdtcount=4 mdscount=2 \\\n    clientdistro=el9.5 serverdistro=el9.5 testgroup=full-dne-zfs-part-3\n\nChange-Id: I9c14d2976bbf66cdf035b0621a2d0bf80c4df860\nSigned-off-by: Jihyeon Gim <potatogim@gluesys.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
